s a reversible comforter in a fun selection of colors, cozy microfiber sheets, and down alternative pillows for a total upgrade.</p>\r\n                </div>\r\n                <div class=\"case toDisplay w-100\">\r\n                    <h2 class=\"mt-5 mb-4 text-light text-uppercase\">DOWN-ALTERNATIVE FILL</h2>\r\n                    <p class=\"text-light\">The hypoallergenic down-alternative fill in our comforter and pillows makes these products cozy all year round—without affecting your allergies.</p>\r\n                </div>\r\n                <div class=\"case toDisplay w-100\">\r\n                    <h2 class=\"mt-5 mb-4 text-light text-uppercase\">DOUBLE-BRUSHED MICROFIBER SHEETS</h2>\r\n                    <p class=\"text-light\">The key to finding a quality microfiber sheet is double brushing and a high GSM rating (grams per square meter). For maximum coziness and an extra-soft touch, our 70 GSM microfiber is the ideal weigh and brushed on each side to produce a velvety texture. </p>\r\n                </div>\r\n\r\n            </div>\r\n            <button id=\"prev\" class=\"bg-transparent pl-0 pr-2\"><i class=\"fa-solid fa-chevron-left\"></i></button>\r\n            <button id=\"next\" class=\"bg-transparent px-2\"><i class=\"fa-solid fa-chevron-right\"></i></button>\r\n\r\n\r\n        </div>\r\n\r\n    </div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"w-75 mx-auto text-center mt-0\" style=\"margin-top: 3rem !important;\">\r\n    <h2>Missing some reviews? No worries </h2>\r\n    <p>it’s mainly due to the pandemic situation disrupting our supply chains. Rest assured, however,<br> that our universally loved bedding will always be deserving of your 5-star review.  </p>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"mt-0 review-counter\" id=\"newreview-section\">\r\n    <div id=\"stamped-main-widget\" data-widget-type=\"one-column\" data-take-reviews='4' data-product-id=\"{{ product.id }}\"></div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n        <div class=\"have-questionsec\">\r\n            <h2>Have questions?</h2>\r\n            <p class=\"quotes\">Here are some frequently asked questions.</p>\r\n        \r\n            <div class=\"question-grid\">\r\n                <div class=\"grid-con\">\r\n                    <div class=\"title-flex\">\r\n                        <img src=\"https://cdn11.bigcommerce.com/s-z2qdisybty/product_images/uploaded_images/question-mark-icon.png?t=1647925466&_gl=1*8pzu4b*_ga*Nzk0NzIwMzUxLjE2NDY2MzgxMzc.*_ga_WS2VZYPC6G*MTY0NzkyNTA4Mi41MS4xLjE2NDc5MjU0NTUuNTU.\" alt=\"\">\r\n                        <h4>Can I use my existing mattress with an adjustable bed base?</h4>\r\n                    </div>\r\n                    <p>Before purchasing, check with the manufacturer of your mattress. Most foam- and innerspring-based mattresses work with an adjustable base. We recommend mattresses between 10” to 12” for best fitting with our bed bases. <br/><br/><a href=\"https://icon-sleep.com/faqs/\" class=\"pl-0 font-weight-bold\">Read More</a></p>\r\n                    \r\n                </div>\r\n                <div class=\"grid-con\">\r\n                    <div class=\"title-flex\">\r\n                        <img src=\"https://cdn11.bigcommerce.com/s-z2qdisybty/product_images/uploaded_images/question-mark-icon.png?t=1647925466&_gl=1*8pzu4b*_ga*Nzk0NzIwMzUxLjE2NDY2MzgxMzc.*_ga_WS2VZYPC6G*MTY0NzkyNTA4Mi41MS4xLjE2NDc5MjU0NTUuNTU.\" alt=\"\">\r\n                        <h4>What is Reach Assist™ on the S755 Adjustable Bed Base?</h4>\r\n                    </div>\r\n                    <p>Malouf’s ultra-luxurious S750 (currently not available here at Icon Sleep) and S755 bed bases have a feature called Reach Assist™, which pulls the bed back toward the wall as you incline for easy access to your nightstand.<br/><br/><a href=\"https://icon-sleep.com/faqs/\" class=\"pl-0 font-weight-bold\">Read More</a></p>\r\n                   \r\n                </div>\r\n                <div class=\"grid-con\">\r\n                    <div class=\"title-flex\">\r\n                        <img src=\"https://cdn11.bigcommerce.com/s-z2qdisybty/product_images/uploaded_images/question-mark-icon.png?t=1647925466&_gl=1*8pzu4b*_ga*Nzk0NzIwMzUxLjE2NDY2MzgxMzc.*_ga_WS2VZYPC6G*MTY0NzkyNTA4Mi41MS4xLjE2NDc5MjU0NTUuNTU.\" alt=\"\">\r\n                        <h4>How does the Snore Detection feature work on the Malouf Base App™?</h4>\r\n                    </div>\r\n                    <p>When a snore is detected for a definite amount of time (which can be preset by the user), the intuitive Malouf Base App™ will automatically move your adjustable bed base to the Anti-Snore position.<br/><br/><a href=\"https://icon-sleep.com/faqs/\" class=\"pl-0 font-weight-bold\">Read More</a></p>\r\n                    \r\n                </div>\r\n                <div class=\"grid-con\">\r\n                    <div class=\"title-flex\">\r\n                        <img src=\"https://cdn11.bigcommerce.com/s-z2qdisybty/product_images/uploaded_images/question-mark-icon.png?t=1647925466&_gl=1*8pzu4b*_ga*Nzk0NzIwMzUxLjE2NDY2MzgxMzc.*_ga_WS2VZYPC6G*MTY0NzkyNTA4Mi41MS4xLjE2NDc5MjU0NTUuNTU.\" alt=\"\">\r\n                        <h4>What is the Malouf Base App™?</h4>\r\n                    </div>\r\n                    <p>The Malouf Base App™ allows users to maximize the health and comfort benefits of sleeping elevated with their adjustable bed base. To learn how to navigate Malouf’s award-winning app, watch this video here: <a href=\"https://youtu.be/SRhVyt94RD4\" class=\"pl-0 font-weight-bold\">https://youtu.be/SRhVyt94RD4</a><br/><br/><a href=\"https://icon-sleep.com/faqs/\" class=\"pl-0 font-weight-bold\">Read More</a></p>\r\n                </div>\r\n            </div>\r\n        </div>\r\n"}
